data.description: Set on almost an acre  of bucolic grounds , welcome to 813 W Kings Highway.  This property has so much to offer. Upon entry you are greeted by an expansive foyer flowing into an oversized living room space which happens to overlook a cozy dining area. Turning left upon entry will lead you to three large bedrooms, one of which will have an ensuite bath.Precede down the hallway to another full bath and large bedroom set in the back of the house. Use the exit door in the living room and step out onto a large patio great for entertaining or just listening to the birds chirp.  A little TLC is needed to make this a real gem. This home is close to schools, major highways and shopping
